idata.python:
rest(beats = 4.5) # rest for half of a beat

# play 2 hi-hat sounds for a fourth of a beat each
playNote(4, beats = 0.25)
playNote(4, beats = 0.25)

rest(beats = 0.5)
playNote(4)
playNote(4)
playNote(4, beats = 0.5)
rest(beats = 0.5) # rest for half of a beat

# play 2 hi-hat sounds for a fourth of a beat each
playNote(4, beats = 0.25)
playNote(4, beats = 0.25)

rest(beats = 0.5)
playNote(4)
playNote(4)
playNote(4, beats = 0.5)
rest(0.5)
# repeat throughout song
playNote(4, beats = 0.25)
playNote(4, beats = 0.25)

rest(beats = 0.5)
playNote(4)
playNote(4)
playNote(4, beats = 0.5)
rest(beats = 0.5) # rest for half of a beat

# play 2 hi-hat sounds for a fourth of a beat each
playNote(4, beats = 0.25)
playNote(4, beats = 0.25)

rest(beats = 0.5)
playNote(4)
playNote(4)
playNote(4, beats = 0.5)
